<l n="b">vikkramākkrā<supplied reason="omitted">n</supplied>ta-vidviṣaḥ</l><!--
seal.1. D. Balogh: Shastri reads prasanna-hr̥dayasaiva, marking only hr̥ as unclear. The facsimile in Shastri is unclear. Given the parallel seals, not known to Fleet, I'm convinced the correct reading is prasanna-tanayasyedaṁ. Sircar_1959-60f:156 suggests the same.
--><lb
n="2"/>
